## Planned Changes

### 1. Move TransactionService + shared models into `aitbc` package

**Problem:** `TransactionService` (Ed25519 signing, balance/nonce queries, signed transaction generation) lives in the Hermes service at `apps/hermes/src/hermes_service/services/transaction_service.py`. The Agent Coordinator already duplicates some of this logic inline in `agent_stream.py` (`_generate_signed_transaction`, `_submit_transaction`). The CLI `coin-requests execute` command imports `TransactionService` and `CoinRequest`/`get_db_session` directly from `hermes_service.*` тАФ a fragile cross-app internal import. Having two implementations of transaction signing is error-prone (the v0.5.8 fee mismatch was partly caused by this split).

**Fix:** Move `TransactionService`, `CoinRequest` model, `CoinRequestStatus` enum, and `get_db_session`/`init_db` into the shared `aitbc` package so both the Agent Coordinator and CLI import from there тАФ no cross-app internal imports.

**Shared package structure:**
```
aitbc/
тФЬтФАтФА crypto/
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА __init__.py
тФВ   тФФтФАтФА transaction_service.py    # TransactionService (moved from hermes_service.services)
тФЬтФАтФА models/
тФВ   тФЬтФАтФА __init__.py
тФВ   тФФтФАтФА coin_request.py           # CoinRequest, CoinRequestStatus (moved from hermes_service.storage)
тФФтФАтФА db/
    тФЬтФАтФА __init__.py
    тФФтФАтФА hermes_db.py               # get_db_session, init_db (moved from hermes_service.storage)
```

**Files changed:**
- `aitbc/crypto/transaction_service.py` тАФ **new** (moved from `hermes_service.services.transaction_service`)
- `aitbc/models/coin_request.py` тАФ **new** (moved from `hermes_service.storage.schema`)
- `aitbc/db/hermes_db.py` тАФ **new** (moved from `hermes_service.storage.database`)
- `apps/agent-coordinator/src/app/websocket/agent_stream.py` тАФ replace inline `_generate_signed_transaction` with `from aitbc.crypto import TransactionService`; replace DB imports with `from aitbc.models import CoinRequest, CoinRequestStatus` and `from aitbc.db import get_db_session`
- `cli/aitbc_cli/commands/coin_requests.py` тАФ change imports from `hermes_service.*` тЖТ `aitbc.*`
- `apps/hermes/src/hermes_service/services/transaction_service.py` тАФ keep for now (Hermes service deleted in ┬з6)

**Env vars:** `BLOCKCHAIN_RPC_URL`, `CHAIN_ID`, `GENESIS_PRIVATE_KEY`, `GENESIS_ADDRESS` тАФ already available to Agent Coordinator via `/etc/aitbc/blockchain.env` and `blockchain-secrets.env`

