### 4. Update CLI to point at Agent Coordinator (8107)

**Problem:** Several CLI commands still default to the Hermes service (8103) or the deprecated coordinator (8203). After the merge, all agent/Hermes commands should hit the Agent Coordinator (8107).

**Fix:**

**4a. `hermes send/receive/peers` (currently 8103):**
These commands hit `/hermes/send`, `/hermes/messages`, `/hermes/peers` on the Hermes service. The Agent Coordinator already has equivalent endpoints тАФ use them directly (no aliases):
- `send` тЖТ `POST /api/v1/agent/messages/send`
- `receive` тЖТ `GET /api/v1/agent/messages/{agent_id}`
- `peers` тЖТ `GET /api/v1/agent/messages/discover`

Update the CLI to use `config.agent_coordinator_url` and these existing endpoint paths. No alias endpoints are added to the Agent Coordinator тАФ this is a breaking change release, external callers should adapt to the canonical API.

**4b. `hermes status/stop/train` (currently 8203/subprocess):**
Removed entirely in ┬з9 тАФ investigation confirmed all training commands are dead code (endpoints don't exist in production, no ML backend).

**4c. `coin-requests execute` hub URL:**
Change `HUB_HERMES_URL` тЖТ `HUB_AGENT_URL` default from `https://hub.aitbc.bubuit.net/api/v1/hermes` to `https://hub.aitbc.bubuit.net/agent` (the Agent Coordinator's public path via nginx).

**4d. Config defaults:**
- `hermes_service_url` тЖТ removed (use `agent_coordinator_url` for all agent commands)
- `coordinator_url` (deprecated 8203) тЖТ removed (only used by status/stop, which are deleted in ┬з9)

**Files changed:**
- `cli/aitbc_cli/config.py` тАФ remove `hermes_service_url`, update/remove `coordinator_url`
- `cli/aitbc_cli/commands/hermes.py` тЖТ `agent.py` тАФ use `agent_coordinator_url` for send/receive/peers with existing endpoint paths
- `cli/aitbc_cli/commands/coin_requests.py` тАФ `HUB_HERMES_URL` тЖТ `HUB_AGENT_URL`

**Tests:**
- Update `tests/cli/test_commands_agent.py` (renamed) to expect 8107 for all commands
- Update `tests/cli/test_commands_agent_training.py` (renamed) to expect 8107

